data.description: Price Improvement 1.19.24… Take a look at our refreshed Kitchen!  New flooring in kitchen, laundry and pantry!  Updated the look of our countertops and new hardware on cabinets!!  Don’t miss out on the opportunity to own a home in the sought after neighborhood of Williamsburg. Featuring 4 Bedrooms, 2.5 Baths, brand new carpet installed just days ago. The open floor plan is great for entertaining family or friends with a large kitchen Island for all to gather around and have some fun!!  Enjoy the outdoors-- this home has a fabulous newer(2021) deck off the kitchen and a large yard for your pets or kids!  Dual Zoned heating/cooling, newer roof (2017), and a Choice Home Warranty should set your mind at ease!!  Seckman High School and walking distance to Antonio Middle.
